description: Retrieves the specified registration field values.

parameters.name: RegistrationId
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the registration.

parameters.name: FieldPaths
parameters.description: An array of paths to the registration form field. (string) ---

nested_items.name: RegistrationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the registration.

nested_items.name: RegistrationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the registration.

nested_items.name: VersionNumber
nested_items.description: The current version of the registration.

nested_items.name: RegistrationFieldValues
nested_items.description: An array of RegistrationFieldValues objects that contain the values for the requested registration.

nested_items.name: FieldPath
nested_items.description: The path to the registration form field. You can use  DescribeRegistrationFieldDefinitions for a list of FieldPaths.

nested_items.name: SelectChoices
nested_items.description: An array of values for the form field.

nested_items.name: TextValue
nested_items.description: The text data for a free form field.

nested_items.name: RegistrationAttachmentId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the registration attachment.

nested_items.name: DeniedReason
nested_items.description: A description of why the registration was denied.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to be used for the next set of paginated results. You don't need to supply a value for this field in the initial request.
